<p align='center'><b>Standardized Experience</b><br>
<b>Course:</b> Learning&emsp;<b>Lective year: <%=@quiz.start_time.to_time.year%></b>&emsp;<b>Level:</b> <%=@quiz.level%>&emsp;<b>Journey:</b> <%=@quiz.journey.id %><br>
